     "text": [
      "\n",
      "=== Fitting LDA Model (5 topics) ===\n",
      "Topic 1: guideline, treatment, cancer, format, mining, patient, process, adherence, evaluate, standard\n",
      "Topic 2: veteran, fatal, opioid, overdose, status, resident, risk, massachusetts, higher, individual\n",
      "Topic 3: supraorbital, hospital, foramen, medical, patient, mart, service, institution, implemented, ict\n",
      "Topic 4: motion, image, provider, artefact, cdws, mri, accuracy, health, individual, exclude\n",
